identification.description: Defines a data provider. The list compiled from the Sub-Annex C to the            2005 ISDA Commodity Definitions ARTICLE XI, Section 11.17. Weather Index Stations or            Locations. Parties may wish to refer to the state meteorological authority in a            particular location or to an exchange or other third party data provider. Parties may            find the definitions in the Commodity Definitions useful as a means of identifying            potential Data Providers.
